    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "@JollyJoker It is limited to <code>+=</code> applied to indirect <code>String</code> references. So first, your array must be a <code>String[]</code>. The issue doesn&#39;t occur with <code>int[]</code>, <code>long[]</code> and friends. But yes, you&#39;re basically right!"
  }, {
