      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "By the way, this applies to the entire left hand side expression, not only the index providing sub-expression. This expression may be arbitrarily complex. See for example <code>IntStream.range(0, 10) .peek(System.out::println).boxed().toArray()[0] += &quot;&quot;;</code>…"
